WEBVTT

00:00.400 --> 00:07.400
Maya: There is another discount that you qualify for, and it's our mobile discount. Who do you have your cell phones with?

00:07.400 --> 00:09.700
Customer: We're with Verizon.

00:10.100 --> 00:12.900
Maya: Great! How many lines do you have?

00:12.900 --> 00:16.000
Customer: We have four lines.

00:16.900 --> 00:20.000
Maya: How much does your cell phone bill cost you each month?

00:20.000 --> 00:23.100
Customer: About five hundred a month.

00:23.900 --> 00:26.600
Maya: Why are you paying so much?

00:26.600 --> 00:29.800
Customer: I... honestly don't know.

00:30.400 --> 00:37.400
Maya: You have four lines, four watches and four iPads at Verizon, and you are paying $500 a month.

00:37.400 --> 00:44.500
Maya: Those four lines, watches and iPads would only cost $185 a month on our Xfinity Mobile Plus plan.

00:45.200 --> 00:52.600
Maya: That would save you $315 each month — that's $3,780 for the first year! Let's get you switched over to Xfinity Mobile right now!

00:52.600 --> 00:55.500
Customer: Let's do it.
